{"tid":117391,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"俾耶徒上司陳紫珊Themis迫害 無左份長俸政府工","createTime":"2017-02-12T07:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T06:02:19.000Z","uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f380991af1de785c0d472ba2ea5c4ca07a3c2d88","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我生長在一個唔食豬的家庭<br />\n阿媽就日日拜五次真主<br />\n但佢地就好鍾意打麻雀<br />\n出到黎做野都唔食豬但就無堅持食清真食品<br />\n係有一次同個天主教徒食飯才知道回教都信耶穌<br />\n不過唔當佢係神的兒子<br />\n咁我有一次同陳紫珊飲茶<br />\n就唔小心講左呢件事出黎<br />\n佢跟住就不斷迫害我<br />\n包括我想自殺入左醫院幾個月佢都迫我跑數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d5515f972d000f18a986c9f43189cc1630b673","tid":117391,"uid":67298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSZnQgoBAqRhiSTEhWgk_ogNMub5i2XaZJGh0FzlVr-b-5g6bca \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSZnQgoBAqRhiSTEhWgk_ogNMub5i2XaZJGh0FzlVr-b-5g6bca%20&h=09130479&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2554080070619b605a729b40d17aa15af7b396c2","tid":117391,"uid":67298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSZnQgoBAqRhiSTEhWgk_ogNMub5i2XaZJGh0FzlVr-b-5g6bca\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSZnQgoBAqRhiSTEhWgk_ogNMub5i2XaZJGh0FzlVr-b-5g6bca&h=ec617f9a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ad77a8268d06a3db8ba990bdf08c9bad6b6d7248","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSZnQgoBAqRhiSTEhWgk_ogNMub5i2XaZJGh0FzlVr-b-5g6bca\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSZnQgoBAqRhiSTEhWgk_ogNMub5i2XaZJGh0FzlVr-b-5g6bca&h=ec617f9a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4c236937eeb52cf4579c5a7de6b67f6340a04c","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763382a818518e3bbc9ea095961ee5b825816965","tid":117391,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:13:37.000Z","msg":"佢驚你係恐怖份子啊"},{"pid":"3e7e09f54849bfaaa4954f9a8f3a205eeaa49c43","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢驚你係恐怖份子啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢之前都知我唔食豬肉啦<br />\n都無迫我辭職"},{"pid":"6d369f02ea31cc4245a88d45be387dc649c49b32","tid":117391,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:17:11.000Z","msg":"睇themis個名都知道係仆街"},{"pid":"000c25c1e39291b19527e066fec090dcf87faa79","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇themis個名都知道係仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法庭個公義女神呀"},{"pid":"4f95b1a1c01fdf185b4ae0373e19c5ed49883972","tid":117391,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇themis個名都知道係仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法庭個公義女神呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢係道貌岸然<br />\n佢係香港嘅岳<del>不群</del>靈珊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725e5d4bc16b71f63f445cd0b13f613cd2dee285","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"唔該幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c1af21e183982db259337d9340793f7b35b870","tid":117391,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5909c842858b52107045f57a30f363461874554","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我情緒不穩，成日要睇心理同精神科<br />\n每朝又嘔返唔到工<br />\n陳紫珊一係叫我辭職去做回教傳道人<br />\n一係話我影響政府運作(我既工作係幫殘疾人士搵工）"},{"pid":"e228cee55115df73ba93c9698263b76b1a061c89","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"我有要求加派人手<br />\n陳紫珊Themis拒絕<br />\n卻不斷要求我辭職<br />\n最後屈我在壹週刊偽造訪問《狀元考試考上癮》事件上係講過唔認<br />\n刺激我情緒<br />\n搞到我當時諗過即刻跳樓自殺<br />\n後來控制住自己<br />\n即刻打辭職信<br />\n咁就無左份工<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"4ba5803e40145854f6f4c78a66aaf05319969e15","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"曾經寫信俾公務員事務局投訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TU7O982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTU7O982.jpg&h=9c5ad9a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U65g4gg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU65g4gg.jpg&h=27db86f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/010122_3806610d1761ef0c31ca96727df48baa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F010122_3806610d1761ef0c31ca96727df48baa.jpg&h=61d16614&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6bf65e01d8c7e805f0115c67f73e8ca72f91d05","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/012638_1054768a8d634ef766c13e8bb5cdd828.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F012638_1054768a8d634ef766c13e8bb5cdd828.jpg&h=06d76e38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0W7r3mb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0W7r3mb.jpg&h=f0480df2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0PU62d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0PU62d.jpg&h=891746dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/012718_ba757c2ebb8af3ae85815725fe1b4755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F012718_ba757c2ebb8af3ae85815725fe1b4755.jpg&h=5abf92d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANaL48h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANaL48h.jpg&h=56396f8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5ddfbdf9da92bb6b2decd261ff315026f7ee00a","tid":117391,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a6bf6dff9b24777f6881ecab1380747223e397","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02c7919462d05503ba7542afbee59ae7a21a814","tid":117391,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係關耶教事咩"},{"pid":"9d7f40c28cf85a245308558ac1756c9ae08ec6c4","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係關耶教事咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個上司係耶人<br />\n佢之前都叫耐唔中幫下我<br />\n雖然成日跣我<br />\n但我講完「回人都信耶穌」之後病左<br />\n佢就成日迫我辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec77c561ada7e032fe5452d2a4a79d811a9e61f0","tid":117391,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:06:43.000Z","msg":"耶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f140abcd09f26edd834b7ab6463c38abfcad529","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>耶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4504a970e704e959f3a07bb25fce8381fff47db7","tid":117391,"uid":37504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:22:21.000Z","msg":"巴打有無諗過係報應？<br />\n當年我親眼睇住個展翅計劃，害左好多細路，佢地會信展翅計劃既，大部分都係基層家庭，自己又無人教育，好多讀完書其實就要立即返工比家用，等屋企人無咁辛苦，好多細路既屋企死慳死抵，比個仔女進修多一兩年。但當年就係你班仆街，推個垃圾展翅計劃，搞到佢地讀完中學最後一次既進修機會比左一個完全無用既展翅。<br />\n<br />\n你有無諗過？個垃圾計劃又害左幾多人既前途？<br />\n<br />\nBtw，你單野好似同耶L無關，而且講來講去，最後都係你on9 resign<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c9023079d06deda4b8252733d708407926b450","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有無諗過係報應？<br />\n當年我親眼睇住個展翅計劃，害左好多細路，佢地會信展翅計劃既，大部分都係基層家庭，自己又無人教育，好多讀完書其實就要立即返工比家用，等屋企人無咁辛苦，好多細路既屋企死慳死抵，比個仔女進修多一兩年。但當年就係你班仆街，推個垃圾展翅計劃，搞到佢地讀完中學最後一次既進修機會比左一個完全無用既展翅。<br />\n<br />\n你有無諗過？個垃圾計劃又害左幾多人既前途？<br />\n<br />\nBtw，你單野好似同耶L無關，而且講來講去，最後都係你on9 resign<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔辭職就會跳樓"},{"pid":"819f93e536d67d379f49f9f4700408b81bb3fc0c","tid":117391,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"between 展翅好似唔收錢喎"}]}